BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 655 Td (Executive Dysfunction:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 240 655 Td (Can't START tasks even when you want to) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 630 Td (Object Permanence:) Tj ET
